  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Keep Girls in School with Period Kits &amp; Toilets</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">When Nigerian girls get their periods, school can be a challenging - even unfriendly - place to learn. Too often, girls miss school during their period because they lack access to affordable period products or safe, private hygiene facilities. Help us transform a school near Abuja into a safe place for girls to thrive. We&apos;ll build toilets, washing stations, and a school library with a spotlight on health/hygiene. We&apos;ll also give every girl two long-lasting PeriodPanties from our partner Be Girl.</narrative>
  </description>
